title: ProGamerManager v0.164b
description: The game is still in active development and will be so for the upcoming 10 months with a planned release in July 2016. Many planned new features will be added every month, we are currently working hard to get Multiplayer, Transfer Market, Player Statistics and an amazing brand new realtime simulation engine into the game, read more about montly feature and content additions on our website. Thanks for supporting us to make this game great and please provide feedback, we would love to hear your opinion. Enjoy the game!
